resources.string:
Izaziso Zomsindo zikusiza ukuthi wazi lokho okwenzakalayo ekhaya lakho.

Lapho Izaziso Zomsindo zivuliwe, ifoni yakho izohlala njalo ihlola imisindo ofuna ukwaziswa ngayo, njengalapho kukhala i-alamu yentuthu noma kukhala ingane.

Izaziso Zomsindo azilokothi zithumele umsindo noma izingxoxo zangemuva ku-Google ngaphandle kwemvume yakho.

I-Live Transcribe ibonisa inkulumo njengombhalo kusikrini sakho ukuze ukwazi ukuhlanganyela ezingxoxweni ezikuzungezile kalula .

Ungathayipha izimpendulo kusikrini ngenkathi ubuke okulotshiweyo, uthole izexwayiso lapho kukhulunywa igama lakho, futhi useshe phakathi nokulotshiweyo.

I-Google icubungula izingxoxo zakho kodwa ayilokothi izigcine.
